Invocation Name: secure pass
des:
Secure Pass is a password generator which provides a random secure password. The password may contain combination of alphanumeric and special characters and if you do not provide password length then the password will default to 8 length. Alexa will read out the password using NATO phonetic alphabet so it's easy to understand and take note. Secure Pass never keeps track or stores the generated passwords. 

Get started now..

"Alexa, ask Secure Pass for a password" 
"Alexa, ask Secure Pass to give me a password" 
"Alexa, open Secure Pass and give me 12 length password"
